             was indicted for <rs id="t18191201-57-off337" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18191201-57-off337" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18191201-57-off337" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18191201-57-cd338" type="crimeDate">30th of October</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18191201-57-off337 t18191201-57-cd338"></join>, one quart pewter pot, value 2 s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18191201-57-victim728" type="victimName">
                     John 
                     Mayne
                  <interp inst="t18191201-57-victim728" type="surname" value="Mayne"></interp>
